txt.en: You have completed 'Deeds of Sant Lhoer, the Poison Gardens'.

After the second downfall of Angmar, the Witch-king of Angmar's realm of old was left all but abandoned. Alas, the remnants of the Iron Crown have crept forth from the shadows and returned to the fortress-city of Carn Dûm, seeking to wield a lost artifact of the Witch-king of Angmar to seize dominion over the Free Peoples of Middle-earth.
